# Development Guide

## Prerequisites

- Python >= {{ python_version }} (managed via UV)
- Node.js >= {{ node_version }} with pnpm
- [Task](https://taskfile.dev/) (task runner)
- {{ container_runtime | title }} and {{ container_runtime | title }} Compose

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install all dependencies
task install

# Start development servers
task dev
```

## Environment Variables

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and configure:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

Key variables:

| Variable | Description | Default |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_ENVIRONMENT` | Environment name | `local` |
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_DEBUG` | Enable debug mode | `false` |
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_DATABASE_URL` | Database connection URL | *(see .env.example)* |
{% if use_redis %}
| `{{ project_slug | upper }}_REDIS_URL` | Redis connection URL | `redis://localhost:6379/0` |
{% endif %}

## Backend Development

```bash
task backend:install    # Install Python dependencies
task backend:dev        # Start backend server
task backend:lint       # Lint with ruff
task backend:format     # Format with ruff
task backend:test       # Run tests via tox
```

## Frontend Development

```bash
task frontend:install   # Install npm dependencies
task frontend:dev       # Start dev server with HMR
task frontend:build     # Production build
task frontend:test      # Run unit tests
task frontend:lint      # Lint with eslint
task frontend:format    # Format with prettier
```

## Docker / Containers

```bash
task docker:up          # Start all services
task docker:down        # Stop all services
task docker:build       # Build images
task docker:logs        # View service logs
```

## Database

```bash
task backend:db:upgrade     # Run migrations
task backend:db:migrate     # Create new migration
task backend:db:seed        # Seed initial data
```

## Testing

```bash
task test               # Run all tests
task backend:test       # Backend tests only
task frontend:test      # Frontend tests only
```

## Code Quality

```bash
task lint               # Lint all code
task format             # Format all code
task typecheck          # Run type checking
```

## pre-commit Hooks

Install hooks:

```bash
pre-commit install
pre-commit install --hook-type commit-msg
```

Run all hooks manually:

```bash
pre-commit run --all-files
```
